    {
      "parameters": {
        "fromEmail": "hello@oddlycraft.com",
        "toEmail": "={{ $json.email }}",
        "subject": "=What actually happens inside an Oddly Craft session?",
        "emailType": "html",
        "message": "=<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<body style=\"margin:0;padding:0;background:#f9f6f1;font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;\">\n<div style=\"max-width:580px;margin:40px auto;background:#ffffff;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;\">\n  <div style=\"background:#1a3a8c;padding:36px 40px;\">\n    <p style=\"color:#ffd234;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 8px;\">Inside Look</p>\n    <h1 style=\"color:#ffffff;margin:0;font-size:24px;font-weight:700;\">\"But I'm not creative\" — we hear this every day.</h1>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"padding:36px 40px;\">\n    <p style=\"color:#444;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;\">And every single time, the person saying it walks out with something they're genuinely proud of. Here's how a session actually works:</p>\n    <ol style=\"color:#444;font-size:15px;line-height:1.9;padding-left:20px;\">\n      <li><strong>You arrive</strong> — we get you set up with your kit</li>\n      <li><strong>You browse</strong> — choose from hundreds of charms or case designs</li>\n      <li><strong>You create</strong> — our team guides you every step of the way</li>\n      <li><strong>You leave</strong> — with a one-of-a-kind piece nobody else has</li>\n    </ol>\n    <p style=\"color:#444;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;\">Sessions run 60–90 minutes and are perfect for date nights, birthdays, team outings, or just a fun afternoon.</p>\n    <div style=\"text-align:center;margin:28px 0;\">\n      <a href=\"https://oddlycraft.com\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:#2249a8;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;\">Book a Session</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "c3d4e5f6-0003-4000-8000-000000000004",
      "name": "Email 2 — How It Works",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.emailSend",
      "typeVersion": 2.1,
      "position": [900, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": { "amount": 2, "unit": "days" },
      "id": "c3d4e5f6-0003-4000-8000-000000000005",
      "name": "Wait 2 Days (2)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.wait",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [1120, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "fromEmail": "hello@oddlycraft.com",
        "toEmail": "={{ $json.email }}",
        "subject": "=Real people, real creations — see what our guests made 🔥",
        "emailType": "html",
        "message": "=<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<body style=\"margin:0;padding:0;background:#f9f6f1;font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;\">\n<div style=\"max-width:580px;margin:40px auto;background:#ffffff;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;\">\n  <div style=\"background:#2249a8;padding:36px 40px;text-align:center;\">\n    <h1 style=\"color:#ffffff;margin:0;font-size:24px;font-weight:700;\">Every piece is unique. Every visit is different.</h1>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"padding:36px 40px;\">\n    <p style=\"color:#444;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;\">At Oddly Craft, no two sessions produce the same result. The charm combination you choose, the case design you draw — it's entirely yours. Here's what some of our recent guests created:</p>\n    <div style=\"text-align:center;margin:24px 0;\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/oddlycraft.malta\" style=\"display:inline-block;\">\n        <img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/66b355473e77ee151ad26afd/855f872f-a835-4359-923c-7d5fad7e2aa0/IMG_9974.JPG\" alt=\"Oddly Craft Creation\" style=\"width:100%;border-radius:12px;\" />\n      </a>\n      <p style=\"color:#888;font-size:12px;margin:8px 0 0;\">Follow us <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/oddlycraft.malta\" style=\"color:#2249a8;\">@oddlycraft.malta</a> for daily inspiration</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:12px;padding:20px;\">\n      <p style=\"color:#2249a8;font-style:italic;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;margin:0;\">&ldquo;I came in thinking I'd make something basic. I left with a bracelet I've worn every day since.&rdquo;</p>\n      <p style=\"color:#888;font-size:13px;margin:8px 0 0;\">— Recent Oddly Craft visitor</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"text-align:center;margin:28px 0;\">\n      <a href=\"https://oddlycraft.com\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:#2249a8;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;\">I Want To Make Something</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>",
        "options": {}
      },
