    {
      "parameters": {
        "fromEmail": "hello@oddlycraft.com",
        "toEmail": "={{ $json.email }}",
        "subject": "=Your questions answered — FAQ about Oddly Craft 💬",
        "emailType": "html",
        "message": "=<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<body style=\"margin:0;padding:0;background:#f9f6f1;font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;\">\n<div style=\"max-width:580px;margin:40px auto;background:#ffffff;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;\">\n  <div style=\"background:#2249a8;padding:36px 40px;\">\n    <h1 style=\"color:#ffffff;margin:0;font-size:24px;font-weight:700;\">Got questions? We've got answers.</h1>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"padding:36px 40px;\">\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom:20px;\">\n      <p style=\"color:#2249a8;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:0 0 6px;\">Q: Do I need any experience?</p>\n      <p style=\"color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;margin:0;\">A: Absolutely not. We guide you through every step. Most first-timers are amazed by what they create.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom:20px;\">\n      <p style=\"color:#2249a8;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:0 0 6px;\">Q: How long does a session take?</p>\n      <p style=\"color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;margin:0;\">A: Between 60 and 90 minutes depending on the activity and how detailed you want to get.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom:20px;\">\n      <p style=\"color:#2249a8;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:0 0 6px;\">Q: What's included in the price?</p>\n      <p style=\"color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;margin:0;\">A: Everything — materials, tools, guidance, and of course your finished creation to take home.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom:20px;\">\n      <p style=\"color:#2249a8;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:0 0 6px;\">Q: Where are you located?</p>\n      <p style=\"color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;margin:0;\">A: Mercury Tower, St. Julian's, Malta. Easy to find with parking nearby.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom:24px;\">\n      <p style=\"color:#2249a8;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:0 0 6px;\">Q: Can I book for a special occasion?</p>\n      <p style=\"color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;margin:0;\">A: Yes! We do birthdays, hen dos, team events, and private sessions. Just contact us and we'll arrange everything.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0;\">\n      <a href=\"https://oddlycraft.com\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:#2249a8;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;\">Ready to Book?</a>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"color:#888;font-size:13px;text-align:center;\">Still have a question? Just reply to this email — we respond within a few hours.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>",
        "options": {}
      },
