    {
      "parameters": {
        "fromEmail": "hello@oddlycraft.com",
        "toEmail": "={{ $json.email }}",
        "subject": "=Last nudge — then we'll leave you in peace 😄",
        "emailType": "html",
        "message": "=<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<body style=\"margin:0;padding:0;background:#f9f6f1;font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;\">\n<div style=\"max-width:580px;margin:40px auto;background:#ffffff;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;\">\n  <div style=\"background:#2249a8;padding:36px 40px;text-align:center;\">\n    <h1 style=\"color:#ffffff;margin:0;font-size:24px;font-weight:700;\">One last thing, {{ $json.firstName }}.</h1>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"padding:36px 40px;\">\n    <p style=\"color:#444;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;\">We've been in your inbox for two weeks now. If you haven't booked yet, that's completely fine — life gets busy.</p>\n    <p style=\"color:#444;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;\">But if Oddly Craft has been sitting in the back of your mind as something you want to try, this is your sign.</p>\n    <p style=\"color:#444;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;\">We genuinely believe that everyone who walks through our door leaves with something they didn't expect: a piece they're proud of, and a surprisingly good time making it.</p>\n    <div style=\"text-align:center;margin:28px 0;\">\n      <a href=\"https://oddlycraft.com\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:#ffd234;color:#1a1a2e;text-decoration:none;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:800;font-size:16px;\">Book Your Session →</a>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"color:#888;font-size:13px;text-align:center;\">After this, you'll only hear from us when we have something genuinely worth sharing — new designs, special offers, or events.</p>\n    <p style=\"color:#888;font-size:13px;text-align:center;\">Thanks for being here. — Team Oddly Craft 💙</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "c3d4e5f6-0003-4000-8000-000000000014",
      "name": "Email 7 — Final Nudge",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.emailSend",
      "typeVersion": 2.1,
      "position": [3100, 300]
    }
